{"title":"信号颂","authors":["郭煌"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":9,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"信号颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻的邮递员呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是什么笑红了你的脸？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮儿在门外旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的嗓音就冲到了我的耳边！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！八届八中全会决议！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字起金光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句亮心间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我兴奋地把报纸摊开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福的蓝图摊在面前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见钢厂在喷射火的瀑布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社里有常绿的春天……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一排排字迹像蓝色的波涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国在决议里拨浪而前！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，祖国所有的高山大川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请都把这决议细听一遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记住这奋战进军的信号："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增产节约，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔向更美的明天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻的邮递员啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你的车快得多么像箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我同你一起去呼喊：祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！跃进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让决议的每个字都变成快马的金鞭！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}